lenders.occupational_info: Welcome to Thomas Gun.We are proud to turn the fashion e-commerce industry upside-down by allowing our customers to purchase directly from the products that our cutting edge brands and retailers choose to offer.Only the best new brands are featured on our website, but each brand has full control over which products they choose to list on our marketplace.This means that customers get the full force of each brand-s creative identity, not just some watered down version offered by a major retailer. Our exciting new business model presents customers with the best designs on the planet - that can be found nowhere else online.We believe at Thomas Gun that customers deserve to choose from an ever-changing range of designs forged by the best talent in fashion while adhering to high standards of brand integrity.Our new fashion commerce model has benefits for both the brand and the customer.Our constant supply of fresh talent allows untried brands to test their products on the market directly while giving customers hot new trends that can-t be found anywhere else.In order to promote brand integrity, at Thomas Gun we-ve carefully considered each brand before selecting them as one of our marketplace retailers.This careful vetting process at the brand level - not the product level - ensures that our customers find only designs they can trust and brands they can rely on.We believe that consumer choice is the only way forward when it comes to fashion, and that means granting customers access to an unedited array of styles and selections designed by the brightest talent available. Gone are the days of boring retail catalogues - at Thomas Gun, our mission is to bring the brands directly to the customers, giving you the best fashion has to offer.
